---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import SEOHead from '../components/SEOHead.astro';
import FocusObject from '../components/FocusObject.astro';
import { url } from '../utils/paths';
---
<Base title="About — Manual Focus, led by James Vickers" description="Marketing agency led by James Vickers. 15+ years senior marketing across endurance and sports brands, AI, fintech and digital assets. Co-founded RGT Cycling (acquired by Wahoo).">
  <SEOHead slot="seo" type="profile" title="About — Manual Focus, led by James Vickers" description="Marketing agency led by James Vickers. 15+ years senior marketing across endurance and sports brands, AI, fintech and digital assets. Co-founded RGT Cycling (acquired by Wahoo)." breadcrumbs={[{ name: 'Home', url: '/' }, { name: 'About', url: '/about' }]} />

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <FocusObject size={300} tiltX={62} tiltY={-18} spin={120} scrollSpin={90} style="top: 4vh; right: 4vw;" />

    <div class="container about-hero-inner">
      <div class="eyebrow">001 · ABOUT</div>
      <h1 class="about-headline" style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6.5vw, 6rem); line-height: 0.95; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-top: var(--space-md); max-width: 900px;">
        Two circles.<br/>
        One <span class="gradient-text">intersection.</span><br/>
        That's where we work.
      </h1>
      <p class="about-lead">
        The Manual Focus mark shows two circles drifting into alignment, marking the point
        where emerging technology meets the markets it changes. AI is changing how people
        find products, digital assets are altering how trust works, and new platforms keep
        creating new rules. The <strong>Foundry</strong>, our collective, and the
        <strong>Forge</strong>, the AI toolkit it built, meet at the same overlap.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO'S BEHIND IT -->
  <section class="about-section section-alt">
    <FocusObject size={220} tiltX={50} tiltY={20} spin={-110} scrollSpin={-80} style="bottom: -40px; left: -40px;" enterFrom="left" />

    <div class="container about-grid">
      <div class="about-grid-side">
        <div class="eyebrow">002 · THE COLLECTIVE</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.75rem); line-height: 0.98; margin-top: var(--space-xs);">Who's<br/>behind&nbsp;it.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="about-grid-body">
        <p>
          Manual Focus is led by <strong>James Vickers</strong>, who has spent over a decade
          running sales, marketing and growth across emerging tech sectors. He co-founded a
          virtual cycling platform that grew to 350,000 users before being acquired by Wahoo
          Fitness, led marketing for a $200M privacy-focused digital asset, and now advises
          AI-powered wealth managers. He has a habit of arriving in these markets before
          mainstream adoption does.
        </p>
        <p>
          Around him, the Foundry brings operators who've led B2B and B2C teams across AI,
          digital assets, fintech and hardware. We ship products, run campaigns and drive
          measurable results from inside the organisations doing the work, not from the
          sidelines. The Forge, our shared AI toolkit, keeps the cycle short.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NUMBERS -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <FocusObject size={260} tiltX={60} tiltY={-15} spin={140} scrollSpin={120} style="top: -40px; right: -40px;" enterFrom="right" />

    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">003 · THE NUMBERS</div>
      <h2 class="about-h2 reveal" style="font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 4.5rem); line-height: 0.98; max-width: 900px;">A track record.<br/><span class="gradient-text">Not a pitch deck.</span></h2>
      <div class="numbers-grid stagger">
        <div class="number-card">
          <div class="number-value"><span class="num-prefix">19k →</span><span class="num-main">350k</span></div>
          <div class="number-label">registered users at RGT Cycling</div>
        </div>
        <div class="number-card">
          <div class="number-value"><span class="num-prefix">−65 →</span><span class="num-main">+45</span></div>
          <div class="number-label">NPS brand turnaround</div>
        </div>
        <div class="number-card">
          <div class="number-value"><span class="num-main">160+</span></div>
          <div class="number-label">media placements, single product launch</div>
        </div>
        <div class="number-card">
          <div class="number-value"><span class="num-prefix">0 →</span><span class="num-main">95</span></div>
          <div class="number-label">brand recall, prompted</div>
        </div>
        <div class="number-card">
          <div class="number-value"><span class="num-prefix">20% →</span><span class="num-main">45%</span></div>
          <div class="number-label">conversion rate improvement</div>
        </div>
        <div class="number-card">
          <div class="number-value"><span class="num-main">2.2M+</span></div>
          <div class="number-label">sessions driven to platform</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY -->
  <section class="about-section section-alt">
    <div class="container about-grid">
      <div class="about-grid-side">
        <div class="eyebrow">004 · WHY WE EXIST</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.75rem); line-height: 0.98; margin-top: var(--space-xs);">Tools change<br/>weekly.<br/><span class="gradient-text">Craft doesn't.</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="about-grid-body">
        <p>
          A new foundation model drops every week and a new AI tool launches every day, so
          most teams struggle to prioritise amid the constant releases. Some freeze, others
          chase everything, and neither approach works.
        </p>
        <p>
          Manual Focus exists because the hard problem isn't access to tools, it's knowing
          which ones matter, when to use them, and how to wire them into your owned, earned
          and paid channels so they actually produce results. We use these tools daily, we
          test the models and we know what's signal and what's noise. We bring marketing
          craft executed at platform speed, without the overhead of a full-time hire.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="about-cta">
    <div class="container about-cta-inner">
      <h2 class="about-cta-headline" style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 5vw, 4rem); line-height: 1; max-width: 900px;">
        Marketing that should<br/>be <span class="gradient-text">working harder</span>?
      </h2>
      <a href={url('/enquire')} class="btn-cta" style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">Start a conversation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  /* ============================
     HERO
     ============================ */
  .about-hero {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-block: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    min-height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-hero-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
  }

  .about-headline {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6.5vw, 6rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .about-lead {
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-width: 680px;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  /* ============================
     SECTIONS
     ============================ */
  .about-section {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-block: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about-h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    align-items: start;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .about-grid-side h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.75rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .about-grid-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .about-grid-body p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .about-grid-body strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .about-lead strong {
    font-weight: 700;
    background: var(--color-cta-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr; gap: var(--space-2xl); }
  }

  /* ============================
     NUMBERS
     ============================ */
  .numbers-grid {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .number-card {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .number-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-text);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .number-value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    line-height: 0.95;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .num-prefix {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.75rem);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .num-main {
    font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 4.5vw, 4rem);
    background: var(--color-cta-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .number-label {
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--font-size-body);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .numbers-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--space-md); }
  }
  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .numbers-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }

  /* ============================
     CTA
     ============================ */
  .about-cta {
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-cta-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .about-cta-headline {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1;
    max-width: 900px;
  }
</style>
